<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ニコキタ教育委員会：ユーザ新規追加</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/account_additionMethod.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #F47B20;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .menu-button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 0.5rem;
        }

        .menu-line {
            width: 24px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }

        .header-title {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .header-user {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 60px);
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .option-button {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            background-color: #E6E6E6;
            border: 2px solid #000080;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .option-button:hover {
            background-color: #D6D6D6;
        }

        .back-button {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background-color: #E6E6E6;
            border: 1px solid #999;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background-color: #D6D6D6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-left">
            <button class="menu-button" aria-label="メニュー">
                <div class="menu-line"></div>
                <div class="menu-line"></div>
                <div class="menu-line"></div>
            </button>
            <h1 class="header-title">ニコキタ教育委員会：ユーザ新規追加</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="header-user">ユーザー：Admin</div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        <h2 class="page-title">追加方法を選択してください。</h2>
        
        <div class="button-container">
            <button class="option-button" onclick="location.href='/account_additionCSV'">CSVファイルで追加</button>
            <button class="option-button" onclick="location.href='/account_addition'">手入力で追加</button>
            <button class="option-button" onclick="location.href='/account_list'">戻る</button>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
